  "id": "hollstein_cloud_detection",
  "summary": "Hollstein decision-tree cloud/cirrus/shadow/snow classification from Sentinel-2 imagery using openEO.",
  "description": "Classifies clouds, cirrus, shadow, water, snow and clear sky from Sentinel-2 L2A reflectance using the Hollstein et al. (2016) decision tree. This titiler variant omits the cirrus band B10 (unavailable in L2A) and substitutes blue/SWIR proxies for the two B10-based tests. Converted from the Sentinel Hub Hollstein evalscript."
}